message: Expanded details on the 11th Division of the Chinese National Revolutionary Army, highlighting its German training, service as the 18th Army during the Second Sino-Japanese War, and its ultimate fate in the Chinese Civil War. Added a 'See also' link to the New 1st Army.
Edited James Breakwell's article to improve neutrality, remove puffery, and add sources for verifiability
